questions.quote: All right, uh... Oh hey, you've done this before Ross, well what did you say when you made up your vows?
Oh, I thought that's what they used to cover Connecticut when it rained.
Y'know what? I am really tired of your bellyaching! Okay, I-I worked really hard at making this a nice place for us to live!
Okay, looks like Ross and I are captains. Okay, so um, I bunnied first so that means I get to pick first. Joey.
Should we go make a baby right now before you change your mind?
Believe me, I've been dreaming about me and Rachel for ten years now. But now, I'm with Julie, so it's like me and Julie, me and Rachel, me and Julie, me and... ... Rachel. Rachel, Rachel.
I'll feel better when I'm there, and I can know where you are all the time.
Oh no. No-no-no, don't do that! How could I live with myself if I knew I was depriving the world of your music.
Well, we just decided that Rachel is gonna be your maid of honor.
Okay, um, don't take this the wrong way, but your place kinda has a weird smell.
